\id 2TH
\h 2 TESALONIKA
\toc1 2 Tesalonika
\toc2 2 Tesalonika
\toc3 2 Tesalonika
\mt1 2 Tesalonika
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Pol, Sailas, Timoti weim,
\p Tesalonika sios, Tamada Negur, Odug Jesus Kristus ado bun ufaregef ã bun, pas enei matotof:
\p 
\v 2 Wau ifenẽya wau inosiya ado, Tamada Negur, Odug Jesus Kristus ado bunem, ã bun ibodõf.
\s1 De Fiyẽya Ado Kosẽya
\p 
\v 3 Turamã tar, amã ã nigin faimud Negur de mafiyẽf bagai, are de age mafiyẽf, ere nigin, ãgenei momoiya fau fau odugef iselef, agog fen, ã ganan abob nigin wauĩ laa fiya anĩ odugef.
\v 4 Anĩ nigin, amã Negur nẽ sios atun, ã momoi ge fen, ã kafĩ fiya darau ganan ado walegef bun to fese gef nigin selĩ kulõ mafedig.
\p 
\v 5 Enei ganan anim, Negur nẽ es fiya are tutuk anĩ yaoref. Anĩ bunem, ã Negur nẽ tano nigin kisi falauf, ã anĩ nigin kafĩ fiya walegef.
\v 6 Negur ĩ madur bagai. Ĩ morõ difeneik anidi morõ ifenẽdiyouf,
\v 7 ã morõ walegef, ĩ karika ifeneĩf, amãg ifanamãf. Anĩ Odug Jesus, in engel megeir adodo geid, yã bale fitotoleya bun saa ilunem isiyouf bun wõ youf.
\v 8 Idi Negur keleĩ sã ado, neda Odug Jesus nẽ biya od to dõ difedig anidi, darau ifenẽdiyouf.
\v 9 Idi daũ fiya faimud ibodkeleya nẽ kafĩ fiya dale fen, Odug mala bun tamal ado, yogon megeir nẽ fula fiya medeĩya bun tamal, irudiyouf.
\v 10 Naa anĩ bun, ĩ isi, yogon fateul tamo kayau bun tamal, fula fiya medeĩya yale di, ĩ nigin momoi den anidi ganan, ĩ nigin meleid yũ yalouf. Are ã gediyouf, ere nigin, ã nemã od nigin momoi gen.
\p 
\v 11 Anĩ nigin amã ã nigin toku kosẽ maudig, are neda Negur iweigneik anĩ kilei, ã kisi feleya inoyeĩf nigin, takag, Negur in megeir bunem, ereb ereb biya ganan ã ago gouf nigin kisi gef anĩ ado, ãgenei momoiya nẽ kabĩ ganan kisi falauf nigin.
\v 12 Amã age ma kosẽ maudig, are neda Negur ado Odug Jesus Kristus neid wau ifenẽya bunem, neda Odug Jesus yana ã atun fula fiya medeĩya yale di, ãg ĩ bun fula fiya medeĩya walogouf nigin age mafedig.
\c 2
\s1 Lo Wal Fiya Tamo Wõ Youf
\p 
\v 1 Turamã tar, Neda Odug Jesus Kristus isiyouf nigin ado, ĩ wagen guru tagauf nigin, amã ã marokeneik,
\v 2 Odug nẽ naa mogo isin yeya anĩ, profet od, wogõya be, pas amã bunem isin ya anĩ karĩg fen, to kaisã terẽg fen, wauĩ kui youf.
\v 3 Naab taka taka bun, taka nem to idegneĩf nigin lo weleg, ere nigin, fau kiwai ketem wõ ye fen, lo wal fiya tamo, are daũ fiya bun ileya nẽ anĩ wõ ye bure fele di, naa are isiyouf.
\v 4 Ĩ kiwai ino fen, ereb ereb ganan waitou de fen, seli dabidig anĩ ĩ farumen ineneĩd fen, ĩ yogo Negur nẽ tempel bun ibod ken, ĩ yogo nigin Negur ye kurõ fesiyouf.
\p 
\v 5 Aya ã geid tabod ken, enei nigin arokeneĩdig anĩ, ã to karĩ welegef de?
\v 6 Gama erebem irounek are ã keleĩ, age fe di, fau yogon sain bun bagai, ĩ wõ youf.
\v 7 Lo wal fiya nẽ waa megeir mogo kabĩ yalef, anĩ ere, ĩ gama irounek anim irouf ile iwaikalauf.
\v 8 Age fe di, lo wal fiya tamo yaorouf, ĩ Odug Jesus in awa yau neseyam yukeis fen, Odug isiya nẽ medeĩya anim ĩ daũ falauf.
\v 9 Lo wal fiya tamo nẽ isiya, de Satan nẽ kabĩ ado susu fel, idegẽya memelik, uris ado, ereb urug bagai fire fire ganan inodiyouf.
\v 10 Agef fen, sesen ganan bunem idi inanakelef anidi idegnẽdiyouf. Idi inanakelef, ere nigin, idi momoi nigin waud laaf fen, kel gei fediyouf anĩ ditoron.
\v 11 Age fiya nigin, Negur idegẽya totol sur fe di, idi anĩ nigin momoi douf.
\v 12 Are idi momoi nẽ nigin to momoi de fen, sesen nigin waud al fen anidi ganan, Negurem es fediyouf nigin age fef.
\s1 Megeir Ifareya
\p 
\v 13 Anĩ ere, amã faimud, ã, turamã tar Odug nẽ oboi nigin, Negur de mafiyẽf bagai, ere nigin, gariya bun, Negur, Awa Uur ã fateul ineneĩya nigin kabĩ yalef bunem ado, ã momoi nẽ nigin momoi gef bunem, kel gei yeĩf nigin igirnein.
\v 14 Ĩ nemã biya od bunem enei bun iweignein, are ã neda Odug Jesus Kristus nẽ fula fiya medeĩya anĩ walogouf nigin age fen.
\v 15 Anĩ nigin, turamã tar, megeir ufareg fen, sigoramam wogõya bunem ado pas bunem, mafelnein anĩ uroug kafĩ walagauf.
\p 
\v 16 Neda Odug Jesus Kristus ĩ yogo ado Tamada Negur, ĩ ada nigin wau laa fen ado, yogon wau ifenẽya bunem, faimud ibodkeleya nẽ wau yaleseya ado wau iseya biya ifanadan anĩ,
\v 17 ã wauĩ yaleseya difenei ken, ereb ereb biya ganan ago gef ado od wogõya bun megeir difeneĩf nigin oromak.
\c 3
\s1 Kosẽ Nigin To Fiya
\p 
\v 1 Od idĩya nigin, turamã tar, Odug nẽ od, ã bun age fef gen, kaisã bagai iyokel fen, tamo kayau atun fula fiya medeĩya yalouf nigin, amã nigin kosẽ gouf.
\v 2 Agog fen, amã tamo idodõya ado sesen bun tamal yalelnamãf nigin kosẽ gouf, ere nigin, tamo gananem momoiya sã.
\v 3 Anĩ ere, Odug ĩ yogon od dõ fiya biya, ĩ ã megeir ifenei ken, Satan bun tamal kulatun yeĩf.
\v 4 Amã Odug bun momoi mauf, are amã ã marokeneik anĩ ago gef ulagauf.
\v 5 Odug ãgenei wauĩ itoneĩ di, Negur nẽ wau laa fiya ado Kristus nẽ feseya sã megeir ifareya bun ilauf nigin oromak.
\s1 Fõ Temeleid Wedereid Irouya
\p 
\v 6 Odug Jesus Kristus yana bunem, turamã tar, amã ã marokeneik, tureĩ tar fõ temeleid ganan, amã mafelnein kilei to mata dibodõdig anidi so wiyẽdigouf.
\v 7 Amã age mafen anĩ naig ge dõ gouf nigin, ã aug keleĩ. Amã ã geid tabodon sain bun, amã to fõ faman.
\v 8 Age ma fen, amã taka nẽ saaf na yaleya sã to mon. Age fiya ban, amã ã atun taka morõ to mafenẽf nigin, bõ ado gaa ado kabĩ totol malen.
\v 9 Amã ã bun tamal isennẽya yaleya kisi feleya, anĩ ere, to age mafen, ere nigin, ã amã bun ulemãg fen, ãg agog dõ gouf nigin.
\v 10 Amã ã geid tabodon sain bun, amã nun enei mafenein: “Taka ĩ kabĩ to yalouf are, ĩ saaf to yãf.”
\p 
\v 11 Amã ã atun tunĩ fõ temeleid yeya anĩ karĩ maun. Idi fõ temeleid, anĩ ere, idi dogo nigin kabĩ to dale fen, taka nigin dogol wogoĩ dedig.
\v 12 Tamo age fediya nigin, Odug Jesus Kristus yana bunem, amã totol bagai moro ken, wedereid marouf, dẽ desil fen, dogo naumeid nigin kabĩ dalouf.
\v 13 Aug nigin, turamã tar, biya ago gouf nigin to fõ yeĩf.
\p 
\v 14 Taka ĩ pas enei bun marokeneik anĩ to dõ fouf are, dẽ wiyẽ kalagauf. Ĩ mama fouf nigin, weim to nigal ũgouf.
\v 15 Anĩ ere, ĩ kiwai gen to ulogouf, ĩ tureĩ gen weder urougauf.
\s1 Idikeleya Nẽ Aanya
\p 
\v 16 Gama wau inosiya nẽ Odug ĩ yogo, sain ganan bun, naab ganan bun, wau inosiya ifeneĩf. Odug ã ganan geid ibodõf.
\p 
\v 17 Aya, Pol, aya imaum aanya enei atotof, are neu pas ganan bun aya yug imauba. Aya eig afe atotodig.
\p 
\v 18 Neda Odug Jesus Kristus nẽ wau ifenẽya ã ganan bun ibodõf. 
